@startwbs
* Dual-Modal Equipment Condition Monitoring Architecture (WBS)
** Web Module
*** Frontend Dashboard (React + Vite)
**** Raw Input Spectrum
**** Fused Frequency Trend
**** System & Hardware Status
*** Frontend-Backend Communication
**** Axios API Client
**** REST API (/api/v1)
*** Backend Interface Layer (FastAPI Routers)
**** Tasks Router (/tasks)
**** Dashboard Router (/dashboard)
**** Models Router (/models)

** Hardware Module
*** Camera Pipeline (UVC)
**** YUY2 160x140@420fps
**** Video frame capture into Capture Service
*** Sensor Pipeline (STM32 IMU)
**** 6-axis sampling ax/ay/az + gx/gy/gz
**** USB CDC serial reporting to IMU Protocol
*** Acquisition and Synchronization
**** Capture Service unified task orchestration
**** Time Sync (Tick Unwrap + linear fitting)

** Model Module
*** Feature Engineering
**** Camera Features (vision_dx/dy_*)
**** IMU Features (sensor_ax...gz_*)
**** Feature Vector Fusion (window alignment + vector construction)
*** Inference and Update
**** Inference Service (state recognition)
**** Model Update Service (incremental update)
*** Storage and Artifacts
**** Task Store (SQLite)
**** Model Registry (SQLite)
**** Feature/Model Artifacts (file storage)
@endwbs
